{"tid":2245614,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打傾下color grading","createTime":"2020-10-16T11:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T11:08:14.000Z","uid":102119,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c30e06ca445280feef207fd8b82d1454e49267ee","tid":2245614,"uid":102119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T11:00:31.000Z","msg":"話說小弟最近幫公司剪片（新手）<br />\n第一次接觸到log (c-log)然後慢慢上網學下撚色<br />\n發覺呢樣野真係好難<br />\n<br />\n啫係我就算令佢變到rec709咁款<br />\n但係我對真係要畀好睇色彩佢呢件事仲係好模糊（係咪叫二級調色）<br />\n有無巴打分享下畀細佬學下野"},{"pid":"88dd63fce5990a10de2f21d1279a0462e8c707f1","tid":2245614,"uid":152147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:03:47.000Z","msg":"要學識睇RGB waveform同vector scope<br />\n利申我新手 都係學緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c12e544cf9596304097c1743fc4a8819d997ef","tid":2245614,"uid":43493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"用緊咩芒"},{"pid":"1d790ce88d77426d2df19d1f62759bbc54b7ded6","tid":2245614,"uid":112855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T04:40:20.000Z","msg":"要快就放個lut變返709再玩色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1576d174cfabc7dce948044dc59ade70c7f665f9","tid":2245614,"uid":204348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T05:51:00.000Z","msg":"最簡單將log轉rec709之後調下光暗 white balance個啲<br />\n之後睇你老細要求你點調"},{"pid":"282710248402d0b7a6d0e6ab5595272340c21bba","tid":2245614,"uid":143402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T01:22:56.000Z","msg":"無人返工慢慢color grading，求其丟個好睇lut就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc2c7733100c1a8f9b650cf6c41e97883f516ebb","tid":2245614,"uid":231725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T20:43:29.000Z","msg":"有無人真係會買lut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e578be16341dbc1b9594cf31c8edcc2d541a94c","tid":2245614,"uid":75722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T20:35:08.000Z","msg":"用 LUT 其實係正路做法嚟<br />\n不過講緊嘅係 Technical LUT 唔係 Look LUT<br />\n同時亦都要搞清楚 Gamma 同 Gamut 嘅分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeccb6770943044622249d23494e2655657c470e","tid":2245614,"uid":102119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e578be16341dbc1b9594cf31c8edcc2d541a94c","tid":2245614,"uid":75722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T20:35:08.000Z","msg":"用 LUT 其實係正路做法嚟<br />\n不過講緊嘅係 Technical LUT 唔係 Look LUT<br />\n同時亦都要搞清楚 Gamma 同 Gamut 嘅分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:04:14.000Z","msg":"呢個我真係唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日見Slog後面會跟個Gamut我真係唔識分"},{"pid":"e49068b1d0f0ed6892b2fb3ef0ce829ab544c7a1","tid":2245614,"uid":75722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aeccb6770943044622249d23494e2655657c470e","tid":2245614,"uid":102119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e578be16341dbc1b9594cf31c8edcc2d541a94c","tid":2245614,"uid":75722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T20:35:08.000Z","msg":"用 LUT 其實係正路做法嚟<br />\n不過講緊嘅係 Technical LUT 唔係 Look LUT<br />\n同時亦都要搞清楚 Gamma 同 Gamut 嘅分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:04:14.000Z","msg":"呢個我真係唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日見Slog後面會跟個Gamut我真係唔識分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"Gamut 係色域<br />\nsGamut 同 sGamut3.cine 拍岀嚟都會唔同顏色<br />\n普通電腦嘅標準色域係sRGB / 成日都聽到嘅Rec.709<br />\n理論上係要用 LUT 去轉換色域 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人都會自己去 boost saturation 嚟代替 LUT<br />\n但好多色域都唔係直線咁「淡色」<br />\n你見好多片膚色都偏黃綠就係 Sony 拍出嚟而冇正確地處理嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e039012a355a999932936860f1568d62c362198b","tid":2245614,"uid":44815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T16:04:35.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"1dc88a6d7fa94c07c740ed80367deac78d031885","tid":2245614,"uid":102119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e49068b1d0f0ed6892b2fb3ef0ce829ab544c7a1","tid":2245614,"uid":75722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aeccb6770943044622249d23494e2655657c470e","tid":2245614,"uid":102119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1e578be16341dbc1b9594cf31c8edcc2d541a94c","tid":2245614,"uid":75722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T20:35:08.000Z","msg":"用 LUT 其實係正路做法嚟<br />\n不過講緊嘅係 Technical LUT 唔係 Look LUT<br />\n同時亦都要搞清楚 Gamma 同 Gamut 嘅分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:04:14.000Z","msg":"呢個我真係唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日見Slog後面會跟個Gamut我真係唔識分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"Gamut 係色域<br />\nsGamut 同 sGamut3.cine 拍岀嚟都會唔同顏色<br />\n普通電腦嘅標準色域係sRGB / 成日都聽到嘅Rec.709<br />\n理論上係要用 LUT 去轉換色域 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人都會自己去 boost saturation 嚟代替 LUT<br />\n但好多色域都唔係直線咁「淡色」<br />\n你見好多片膚色都偏黃綠就係 Sony 拍出嚟而冇正確地處理嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多少少<br />\n上次同事用slog2拍<br />\n我都係套返lut轉做709<br />\n但其實我見有時D709 lut都有幾個版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5972c54349cf19de379c8116488f1ffbb7ee6933","tid":2245614,"uid":75722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1dc88a6d7fa94c07c740ed80367deac78d031885","tid":2245614,"uid":102119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e49068b1d0f0ed6892b2fb3ef0ce829ab544c7a1","tid":2245614,"uid":75722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aeccb6770943044622249d23494e2655657c470e","tid":2245614,"uid":102119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T08:04:14.000Z","msg":"呢個我真係唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日見Slog後面會跟個Gamut我真係唔識分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"Gamut 係色域<br />\nsGamut 同 sGamut3.cine 拍岀嚟都會唔同顏色<br />\n普通電腦嘅標準色域係sRGB / 成日都聽到嘅Rec.709<br />\n理論上係要用 LUT 去轉換色域 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人都會自己去 boost saturation 嚟代替 LUT<br />\n但好多色域都唔係直線咁「淡色」<br />\n你見好多片膚色都偏黃綠就係 Sony 拍出嚟而冇正確地處理嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多少少<br />\n上次同事用slog2拍<br />\n我都係套返lut轉做709<br />\n但其實我見有時D709 lut都有幾個版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T17:36:30.000Z","msg":"709 LUT 有好多個版本<br />\n係因爲正統 709 係等於平時新聞片嘅顏色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上呢個年代冇人會鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以 Sony Official LUT 爲例<br />\nRec 709 (800%)，即係比正常 709 可以顯示更多 Highlight 嘅 LUT<br />\nLC709 係 Low Contrast 709 咁解<br />\n而佢個 LC709 Type A 顧名思義就係扮 Alexa <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCine + 709 係加返少少 contrast 去 Match Sony 啲 Cine Profile，<br />\n再將個顏色轉返去 709 Standard<br />\n<br />\n如果你用開 Resolve 嘅話，<br />\n可以搵吓內置有個叫 Color Space Transform 嘅 OFX plugin，<br />\n呢個係更加正路嘅做法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩唔明可以再問"},{"pid":"68ac6a10e2b980c163ec9ca97cff8faeab8f6541","tid":2245614,"uid":244832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5972c54349cf19de379c8116488f1ffbb7ee6933","tid":2245614,"uid":75722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1dc88a6d7fa94c07c740ed80367deac78d031885","tid":2245614,"uid":102119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e49068b1d0f0ed6892b2fb3ef0ce829ab544c7a1","tid":2245614,"uid":75722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T10:33:08.000Z","msg":"Gamut 係色域<br />\nsGamut 同 sGamut3.cine 拍岀嚟都會唔同顏色<br />\n普通電腦嘅標準色域係sRGB / 成日都聽到嘅Rec.709<br />\n理論上係要用 LUT 去轉換色域 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人都會自己去 boost saturation 嚟代替 LUT<br />\n但好多色域都唔係直線咁「淡色」<br />\n你見好多片膚色都偏黃綠就係 Sony 拍出嚟而冇正確地處理嘅嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多少少<br />\n上次同事用slog2拍<br />\n我都係套返lut轉做709<br />\n但其實我見有時D709 lut都有幾個版本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T17:36:30.000Z","msg":"709 LUT 有好多個版本<br />\n係因爲正統 709 係等於平時新聞片嘅顏色 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上呢個年代冇人會鍾意睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以 Sony Official LUT 爲例<br />\nRec 709 (800%)，即係比正常 709 可以顯示更多 Highlight 嘅 LUT<br />\nLC709 係 Low Contrast 709 咁解<br />\n而佢個 LC709 Type A 顧名思義就係扮 Alexa <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nCine + 709 係加返少少 contrast 去 Match Sony 啲 Cine Profile，<br />\n再將個顏色轉返去 709 Standard<br />\n<br />\n如果你用開 Resolve 嘅話，<br />\n可以搵吓內置有個叫 Color Space Transform 嘅 OFX plugin，<br />\n呢個係更加正路嘅做法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有咩唔明可以再問"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T19:01:28.000Z","msg":"師兄講得好有心"},{"pid":"4b898ded7b6bc579efec5a04a7ee0925c37857b8","tid":2245614,"uid":75722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68ac6a10e2b980c163ec9ca97cff8faeab8f6541","tid":2245614,"uid":244832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5972c54349cf19de379c8116488f1ffbb7ee6